Prepare grill for indirect method, coat with cooking spray. Brush the turkey with the vegetable oil. Combine garlic salt and chili powder; sprinkle over turkey. Place turkey on grill. Cover grill and cook according to package directions. To make salsa: Combine tomatoes, onions, cilantro, vinegar, olive oil, salt and pepper. Chill until time of serving. Serve with sliced, grilled turkey.